  <brief_title>Use of Omega 3 Oil Emulsion for Parenteral Nutrition Associated Cholestasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Trial of Omegaven™ Therapy for Parenteral Nutrition Associated Cholestasis</official_title>
